<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2607866>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–5. Poreuomenini Brunner von Wattenwyl, 1878. Habitus in lateral view of Poreuomena sanghensis Massa, 2013 (1), Cestromoecha crassipes (Karsch, 1890) (2), Cestromoecha longicerca Massa, 2013 (3), stridulatory area of Poreuomena lamottei Chopard, 1954 (4) and Cestromoecha crassipes (5)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2607866/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2607870>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15–18. Habitus in lateral view of Gravenreuthia saturata Karsch, 1892 (15), Zeuneria longicercus Sjöstedt, 1929 (16), Mangomaloba latipennis Chopard, 1954 (17), and Morgenia hamuligera Karsch, 1890 (18)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2607870/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

